The amount of discipline that you give yourself is very important for a healthy life. Therefore, we must be aware of how much we give to ourselves and if we’re doing it in a healthy way.
Write out a day plan on what you would like to do today and see if you’ve completed your plan by the end of the day.
Today is Nine Days, which is One Week and Two Days of the Omer.
Hayom yom sheni sh’b’shavuah echad la’omer.